<codeline lineno="14"><highlight class="comment">module<sp/>into<sp/>your<sp/>query,<sp/>and<sp/>associate<sp/>the<sp/>specified<sp/>prefix<sp/>(in<sp/>this</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="15"><highlight class="comment">case<sp/>&quot;file&quot;)<sp/>with<sp/>the<sp/>URI<sp/>of<sp/>the<sp/>module.<sp/>You<sp/>can<sp/>then<sp/>utilize<sp/>these</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="16"><highlight class="comment">functions<sp/>in<sp/>your<sp/>query:</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="17"><highlight class="comment"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="18"><highlight class="comment">\code</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="19"><highlight class="comment">import<sp/>module<sp/>namespace<sp/>file<sp/>=<sp/>&quot;http://expath.org/ns/file&quot;;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="20"><highlight class="comment"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="21"><highlight class="comment">if<sp/>(file:is-file(&quot;foo.txt&quot;))</highlight></codeline>
