<codeline lineno="23"><highlight class="comment">else<sp/>()</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="24"><highlight class="comment">\endcode</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="25"><highlight class="comment"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="26"><highlight class="comment">You<sp/>may<sp/>import<sp/>as<sp/>many<sp/>modules<sp/>as<sp/>you<sp/>wish,<sp/>so<sp/>long<sp/>as<sp/>each<sp/>is<sp/>at<sp/>a</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="27"><highlight class="comment">unique<sp/>URI<sp/>and<sp/>is<sp/>associated<sp/>with<sp/>a<sp/>unique<sp/>prefix.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="28"><highlight class="comment"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="29"><highlight class="comment">&lt;a<sp/>href=&quot;../../../download&quot;&gt;Please<sp/>check<sp/>here&lt;/a&gt;<sp/>for</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="30"><highlight class="comment">more<sp/>information<sp/>about<sp/>importing<sp/>\ref<sp/>non_core_modules.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="31"><highlight class="comment"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="32"><highlight class="comment">Note:<sp/>the<sp/>URI<sp/>specified<sp/>to<sp/>&lt;tt&gt;import<sp/>module&lt;/tt&gt;<sp/>will<sp/>be<sp/>resolved<sp/>by</highlight></codeline>
